{"title_page": "Mookkannoor Govt. Higher Secondary School", "text_new": "{{Use dmy dates|date=January 2020}}\n{{Use Indian English|date=January 2020}}\n{{Infobox school\n| name              = Mookkannoor Govt. Higher Secondary School\n| native_name       = \n| image             = Govt HSS Mookkannoor, Kerala, India.jpg\n| image_size        = \n| alt               = Main campus of Mookkannoor Govt HSS\n| caption           = Main campus of Mookkannoor Govt HSS\n| logo              = \n| pushpin_map       = India Kerala#India\n| coordinates       = {{Coord|10|12|49.65|N|76|24|18.21|E|display=title}}\n| motto             = \n| established       = 1931\n| location          = Mookkannoor\n| closed            = \n| type              = Higher Secondary\n| status            = \n| category_label    = \n| category          = \n| gender_label      = \n| gender            = Boys and Girls\n| affiliation       = Govt. of Kerala\n| affiliations      = \n| administrator     = \n| assst_admin       = \n| president         = \n| chairman_label    = \n| chairman          = \n| rector            = \n| principal         = \n| asst principal    = \n| campus_director   = \n| headmaster        = \n| head_name         = \n| head              = \n| head_name2        = \n| head2             = \n| dean              = \n| founder           = \n| chaplain          = \n| officer_in_charge = \n| faculty           = \n| teaching_staff    = \n| enrollment        = \n| grades_label      = \n| grades            = \n| streetaddress     = \n| city              = [[Mookkannoor]]\n| state             = [[Kerala]]\n| province          = \n| country           = [[India]]\n| district          = [[Ernakulam District]]\n| oversight         = \n| accreditation     = \n| campus            = \n| colors            = \n| colours           = \n| athletics         = \n| houses            = \n| student_union     = \n| nickname          = \n| mascot            = \n| free_label        = \n| free_text         = \n| rival             = \n| yearbook          = \n| newspaper         = \n| free_label_1      = \n| free_1            = \n| free_label_2      = \n| free_2            = \n| free_label_3      = \n| free_3            = \n| test_name         = \n| test_average      = \n| national_ranking  = \n| website           = https://schoolwiki.in/25027\n| footnotes         = \n| picture           = \n| picture_caption   = \n| picture2          = \n| picture_caption2  = \n}}\n'''Mookkannoor Govt. Higher Secondary school''' is a school situated at [[Mookkannoor|Mookkannoor Gram Panchayath]], [[Ernakulam district|Ernakulam District]], [[Kerala]], [[India]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://lsgkerala.in/mookkannurpanchayat/history/|title=\u0d2e\u0d42\u0d15\u0d4d\u0d15\u0d28\u0d4d\u0d28\u0d42\u0d30\u0d4d\u200d \u0d17\u0d4d\u0d30\u0d3e\u0d2e\u0d2a\u0d1e\u0d4d\u0d1a\u0d3e\u0d2f\u0d24\u0d4d\u0d24\u0d4d (Mookkannur Grama Panchayat) \u00bb \u0d1a\u0d30\u0d3f\u0d24\u0d4d\u0d30\u0d02}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://sv1.mathrubhumi.com/education/schools/Govt._H._S._S._Mokkannoor/1284/|title=Govt. H. S. S. Mokkannoor|website=Mathrubhumi Education}}</ref> The school is situated in Angamaly assembly constituency.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://sametham.kite.kerala.gov.in/publicView/schools/25027|title=Sametham - Kerala School Data Bank.|website=sametham.kite.kerala.gov.in}}</ref><ref name=\"auto\">http://www.niyamasabha.org/codes/14kla/session_11/ans/u02767-180618-907000000000-11-14.pdf</ref> The school was established on 1931.<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.education.kerala.gov.in/downloads2014/statistics/ekmstat1892017.pdf|title=List of Schools in Ernakulam District|last=|first=|date=|website=www.education.kerala.gov.in|url-status=live|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=2019-12-07}}</ref> The school is situated near by St. Mary's Forane church in [[Angamaly]]-[[Ezhattumugham, Kerala|Ezattumugham]] Road.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://ernakulam.nic.in/public-utility-category/schools/page/5/|title=Schools &#124; Ernakulam District Website &#124; India}}</ref>  \n==History==\nThe school was started as in 1913.<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.education.kerala.gov.in/downloads2014/statistics/ekmstat1892017.pdf|title=List of Schools in Ernakulam District|last=|first=|date=|website=www.education.kerala.gov.in|url-status=live|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=2019-12-07}}</ref> by St. Marys Church.<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://lsgkerala.in/mookkannurpanchayat/history/|title=\u0d2e\u0d42\u0d15\u0d4d\u0d15\u0d28\u0d4d\u0d28\u0d42\u0d30\u0d4d\u200d \u0d17\u0d4d\u0d30\u0d3e\u0d2e\u0d2a\u0d1e\u0d4d\u0d1a\u0d3e\u0d2f\u0d24\u0d4d\u0d24\u0d4d (Mookkannur Grama Panchayat) \u00bb \u0d1a\u0d30\u0d3f\u0d24\u0d4d\u0d30\u0d02|access-date=2019-12-07}}</ref>\n\n==Amenities==\nAll high school and higher secondary school as now upgraded to smart class rooms by KITES.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://survey.kite.kerala.gov.in/index.php/welcome/allschools_districtwise/|title=HIGH TECH SCHOOL|website=survey.kite.kerala.gov.in|access-date=2019-12-07}}</ref>\n\n==Curriculum==\nThe school follows Kerala State Syllabus of Education (SCERT) for classes from 1th to 12th.<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://dhsekerala.gov.in/schoolist.aspx?dcode=07|title=schoolist|website=dhsekerala.gov.in}}</ref> In 2012 the school scored 100% victory in SSLC Examination.<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.thehindu.com/news/cities/Kochi/sslc-results-good-show-by-government-schools/article3359812.ece|title=SSLC results: good show by government schools|last=Reporter|first=Staff|date=2012-04-27|work=The Hindu|access-date=2019-12-07|language=en-IN|issn=0971-751X}}</ref>\n\n==Buildings==\nThe school has two double storied buildings and a single storied building.\n\n==Notable Alumni==\n*[[K.P Hormis|K P Hormis]] <ref>{{Cite web|url=http://kphormisecs.org/about.aspx|title=kphormisecs &#124; About|website=kphormisecs.org}}</ref>\n==Gallery==\n<gallery mode=\"nolines\">\nFile:Govt HSS Mookkannoor HSS Campus, Kerala, India.jpg|Higher Secondary Campus\nFile:Mookkannoor Govt HSS Mookkannoor, Kerala, India.jpg|Main Gate\nFile:Govt Higher Secondary School Mookknnoor 1.JPG|Side View\nFile:Govt HSS main block, Mookkannoor, Kerala, India.jpg|Main Block\nFile:Mookkannoor Govt HSS second block, Mookkannoor, Kerala, India.jpg|Second Block\nFile:Govt HSS third block, Mookkannoor, Kerala, India.jpg|Third Block\n</gallery>\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==See also==\n*[[List of schools in Ernakulam district]]\n*[[SSLC]]\n*[[Secondary School]]\n*[[Education in Kerala]]\n\n{{Education in Kerala}}\n\n[[Category:Schools in Ernakulam district]]\n[[Category:High schools and secondary schools in Kerala]]\n", "text_old": "{{Use dmy dates|date=January 2020}}\n{{Use Indian English|date=January 2020}}\n{{Infobox school\n| name              = Mookkannoor Govt. Higher Secondary School\n| native_name       = \n| image             = Govt HSS Mookkannoor, Kerala, India.jpg\n| image_size        = \n| alt               = Main campus of Mookkannoor Govt HSS\n| caption           = Main campus of Mookkannoor Govt HSS\n| logo              = \n| pushpin_map       = India Kerala#India\n| coordinates       = {{Coord|10|12|49.65|N|76|24|18.21|E|display=title}}\n| motto             = \n| established       = 1931\n| location          = Mookkannoor\n| closed            = \n| type              = Higher Secondary\n| status            = \n| category_label    = \n| category          = \n| gender_label      = \n| gender            = Boys and Girls\n| affiliation       = Govt. of Kerala\n| affiliations      = \n| administrator     = \n| assst_admin       = \n| president         = \n| chairman_label    = \n| chairman          = \n| rector            = \n| principal         = \n| asst principal    = \n| campus_director   = \n| headmaster        = \n| head_name         = \n| head              = \n| head_name2        = \n| head2             = \n| dean              = \n| founder           = \n| chaplain          = \n| officer_in_charge = \n| faculty           = \